No unnecessary duplication.

Problem 4: Updating Data is Difficult

Suppose Rahul changes branch.

File System

Need to update:

students.txt
library.txt
hostel.txt
fees.txt

If one file is missed:

Data becomes incorrect.

DBMS

Update only one record:

UPDATE Student
SET Branch='IT'
WHERE Student_ID=101;

Done.

Everywhere updated.

